In the distance, a few taller buildings punctuate the skyline, their silhouettes standing out against the azure backdrop. The sun, positioned in the top right corner of the image, casts its bright light over the scene, illuminating the cityscape with a warm glow. 

The street itself is lined with trees, their green foliage adding a touch of nature to the urban setting. A few cars can be seen on the road, hinting at the city's active life. In the far distance, a crane is visible, perhaps indicative of ongoing construction or development in the city. 

Overall, the image provides a comprehensive view of a day in the life of Beijing, capturing the city's architectural charm and dynamic street life.
